Description: The `centrimpact` R package provides a comprehensive toolkit for analyzing and visualizing community engaged research metrics as highlighted in the CEnTR*IMPACT framework. It offers specialized functions for researcher-partner alignment, project dynamics, cascade effects, and creating publication-ready visualizations.
